{"tid":990450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣爵悅庭一房610萬元沽 屋苑2個月高","createTime":"2019-01-21T15:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T16:45:56.000Z","uid":33886,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcb44dcba408919b66b6af48b62d9fb060aa520","tid":990450,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"中原地產荃灣區高級資深區域營業董事謝秋儀表示，爵悅庭新近錄得東爵(A1座)中層H單位成交，單位實用面積384平方呎，建築面積510平方呎，一房間隔，剛以610萬元沽出，平均實用呎價15,885元，屬近兩個月的新高價，同類型單位近日最低成交價為約581萬元。<br />\n<br />\n謝秋儀表示，原業主則於2016年以480萬元買入單位，持貨3年，帳面獲利130萬元，升值27%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2255942/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%88%B5%E6%82%85%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF610%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD%20%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%912%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%AB%98?mtc=90025&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2255942%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2588%25B5%25E6%2582%2585%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2588%25BF610%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25B2%25BD%2520%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%258B%25912%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%25AB%2598%3Fmtc%3D90025%26utm_source%3Dcopy%26utm_campaign%3Dios%26utm_medium%3Dshare&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4In26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f20dd408\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2255942/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%88%B5%E6%82%85%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%80%E6%88%BF610%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD%20%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%912%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%AB%98?mtc=90025&amp;utm_source=copy&amp;utm_campaign=ios&amp;utm_medium=share</a>"},{"pid":"d1f9970dddc5cc147e3b6beaec6265ddebff4ca6","tid":990450,"uid":83582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"工廠三寶全廠景同市景個價可以差好遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9f6ca813a61d18924b8e6d3d4110b94a72787b","tid":990450,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d1f9970dddc5cc147e3b6beaec6265ddebff4ca6","tid":990450,"uid